<br>
If any mage at 55 is feared that easily, they deserve to die.  Any 55+ mage should be able to get thier mr 100+ unbuffed.  At that range, a mage should be able to resist fear 95% of the time.<br>
<br>
Actually, killing necros that think this way is easy.  While they are wasting mana attempting to fear your pet (you put 2x dagger of symbols and and the resist shoulders on your pet, right), you pet is tearing through thier pet.  If the necro continues to try fearing, do nothing but nuke the necros ass till he/she dies.<br>
<br>
The only scarey necro is one that only uses fast casting life taps as thier offense coupled with a pet.  Even this is combatable with scars at level 54+.  Just stay out of normal casting range and bolt him every chance you get....if he has a pet up, just let the pets duke it out as yours will eventually win. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ubunchkles.showPublicProfile?language=EN>bunchkles</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#333333>(6/19/02 9:21:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=85.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Necro vs mage...</span><hr size=1> did he say &quot;fear pet&quot;?<br>
